{"tid":1592082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非行動]寫信，Letter to the world（重開）","createTime":"2019-09-24T12:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T18:07:26.000Z","uid":202895,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96bdcebcc2a90a5f7b4fec0d2408405073eeccaa","tid":1592082,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"有人話我地文宣攻勢差咗，<br />\n我就諗起之前有一個Post係講寄信去中國，傳播革命思想<br />\n咁我呢個傻仔就突然認為可以試下嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係可以試下擴大一下範圍，<br />\n呢個叫Letter to the world活動<br />\n好似漂流瓶呢種方式咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n活動內容：寫信<br />\n<br />\n題目：反送中活動至今已超過100天，為把心聲傳到世界各地的人民手中。試以香港人的名義，撰寫信件一封，先說明反送中活動的內容，再以香港人的身份角度抒發個人感受，並舉出為何他們應支持我們的原因，加以論證，最後，建議他們支持我們的方法（如杯葛當地共匪公司，如有當地聲援活動，則需提及。）<br />\n<br />\n文體：不限（抒情/說明均可）<br />\n<br />\n語言：不限<br />\n<br />\n地點：不限（隨機派送）<br />\n<br />\n頻率：建議一日一封（昐望能持久發展，而熱情亦可保持）<br />\n<br />\n其他：<br />\n*書信結尾請呼籲佢地若收到，請去twitter Post收到嘅照片同 hashtag#LetterfromHK，睇下可唔可以相認。<br />\n<br />\n*寄信時可以hashtag#Lettertotheworld，以便統計人數及造勢。<br />\n<br />\n***本次測驗不容許抄襲，copy template等等作弊手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，書信貴在溫度，原創性，可以抄自己，但唔好copy報章，他人原創等。<br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人想了解香港人心聲更多，而唔係新聞內容，所以儘量講多小小個人感受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知道會唔會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，會唔會有人響應，但係我地唔做係永遠唔會成功。<br />\n呢個活動亦都係提供一D危險性低嘅活動比老人家，小朋友參加。<br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"824bd8edc59a37c97f0b778d2f3ac205fc7826bf","tid":1592082,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"重開，上個Post連一個人都冇"},{"pid":"e870b99d0471855c74319ebd9156c328374b1cb6","tid":1592082,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"6b649833c7f55c628f576e455ddbec2035ad6b50","tid":1592082,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:35:04.000Z","msg":"咁呢樣野係人人可以參與嘅，<br />\n雖然係膠膠D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係我認為幾老少咸宜嘅活動黎<br />\n仲有自己寫一封，每日印一封去寄就OK啦<br />\n仲可以隨信附送靚靚文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e8a9dec15d0ecde148429cd56e435990d95810e","tid":1592082,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我需要人"},{"pid":"30cd5650d94864967e8bc0aea576c9c0742879ee","tid":1592082,"uid":287557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dM4v5Aa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdM4v5Aa.png&h=1d3926f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97tAxfb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97tAxfb.png&h=3f0a0a65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9cf3829bc4727c2d475ad6ea3bb1cdf8e0f3aad","tid":1592082,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重開都冇人ge"},{"pid":"5bfc7f7613ed1361716d7f96935e3eafab2d6388","tid":1592082,"uid":146583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"927 新屋嶺遮打集會<br />\n928港島連儂牆 民陣添馬公園集會<br />\n929 全球反極權遊行<br />\n930 全港大三罷<br />\n101 國殤黑衣日"},{"pid":"8c43e6e50a99b6bdcd81ce16b6864e86ae00ef3f","tid":1592082,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T12:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啊啊啊"},{"pid":"450764db1b8e28c